    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car has been pampered like a member of the family\u2014it looks and feels exactly like it did the day it left the showroom. It's been garage-kept, smoke-free, and the interior is absolutely spotless. You really have to see this one in person to believe how pristine it is. I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
