    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It has been my pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with hand washes every single weekend. It honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or blemish to be found! If you're looking for a ride that's in truly pristine, flawless condition, you\u2019ve found it. Come see it for yourself; I promise you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
