    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a definitive example of the 993-generation Carrera, featuring the final evolution of the air-cooled 3.6L M64 flat-six engine. This unit utilizes the Varioram induction system for optimized torque across the rev range, mated to a Getrag G50 6-speed manual transaxle with a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, retaining original kinematics with a multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson strut front end. Braking performance is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled, ventilated rotors. This vehicle displays zero oil seepage, perfect compression across all cylinders, and a pristine undercarriage. A turn-key, investment-grade machine for the air-cooled purist.",
